videos.description: Chris Lykes finds Dewan Huell who lays it up and draws the foul for Miami.
videos.headline: Lykes drops dime to Huell who gets the and-1

videos.description: Chris Lykes tips a pass to himself and quickly lays it up on the other end while drawing the foul for Miami.
videos.headline: Lykes scores a speedy and-1

videos.description: Nikola Djogo gets a bounce pass to TJ Gibbs who lays it up to cut Miami's lead.
videos.headline: Notre Dame answers with Gibbs layup

videos.description: Matt Farrell makes a long jumper for Notre Dame to tie the game in the second half.
videos.headline: Farrell ties game with long 3-pointer

videos.description: Ebuka Izundu blocks a shot to keep Miami in the lead late against Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Izundu shuts down Notre Dame with block

videos.description: Ebuka Izundu grabs the offensive rebound an puts it back up to extend Miami's lead.
videos.headline: Izundu comes up with putback bucket

videos.description: Ebuka Izundu jumps up for the offensive board and puts it back up to keep Miami's lead with just seconds left vs. Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Miami solidifies win with Izundu putback bucket
